replies.body:
Hi littlemisscheeky,

I saw you @ OPL finals presenting the fan art winners. Just wanted to say I love your hair! So rad!

Two questions;

1. Do you... have a bf? {{champion:32}} 
2. Is your name pronounced "eye-rene" or "i-reeeen"? 
I think eye-rene sounds way better, don't you? {{champion:17}}
